      "location": "src/odoo_forge/project_catalog/resolver.py:34",
      "severity": "WARNING",
      "claim": "_matched_by relies on the implicit field-declaration order of ProjectCatalogRequest to build the '+'-joined matched_by string. The coupling is not expressed by name, comment, or type, so reordering the model fields silently changes the public matched_by contract that the tests assert.",
